high_descs: pick up the fork that is in front of the sink
move two steps to the left
put the fork in the sink, fill with water, take fork out
turn to the left to face counter
put the fork in the drawer
pick up fork from sink edge
wash and remove fork from sink
turn left to face counter tops and drawers
Turn right and walk to the sink,
Pick up the fork that's in front of you on the counter.
Take a step to your left then a step back.
Wash the fork in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left to face the counter.
Open the drawer under the counter to the right of the stove and put the fork in there then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.
